    "description": "<i>Bub Block</i> is a chaotic local multiplayer game where dodging spinning death traps is only half the fun. The real trick is trapping your friends before they trap you!<br><br>Drop blocks to box in opponents, survive the ever-shrinking arena, and even come back from the dead as a ghost seeking revenge.<br><br>Every match is customizable chaos. Tweak block limits, blade speeds, punching rules, and more for your perfect game night setup. Play locally on the couch, via Steam Remote Play Together, or invite friends online (no public lobbies yet).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br>⚔️ Local multiplayer mayhem for 2-4 players<br><br>🧱 Drop blocks to trap friends (or yourself!)<br><br>⚡ Spinning blades and other hazards (available in the DLC)<br><br>👻 Ghost mode lets you haunt players after death<br><br>🛠️ Full match customization: speed, blocks, abilities, and more<br><br>🕹️ Works seamlessly with Remote Play Together<br><br>🌐 Limited online play via private invites (no public matchmaking yet)",
